000 intelligence reports each year, far more than the government can effectively digest. The US is running so many secret programs that James R. Clapper Jr., director of national intelligence, said during his confirmation hearings that 'only one entity in the entire universe' knows what they're all doing, and 'that's God.'\"<p><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.slashdot.org%2Fstory%2F10%2F10%2F29%2F1657248%2FAnnual-US-Intelligence-Bill-Tops-80-Billion%3Ffrom%3Dfb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><img src=\"http://a.fsdn.com/sd/facebook_icon_large.png\"></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/home?status=Annual+US+Intelligence+Bill+Tops+%2480+Billion%3A+http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F9EG463\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><img src=\"http://a.fsdn.com/sd/twitter_icon_large.png\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://news.slashdot.org/story/10/10/29/1657248/Annual-US-Intelligence-Bill-Tops-80-Billion?from=rss\">Read more of this story</a> at Slashdot.</p><iframe src=\"http://slashdot.org/slashdot-it.pl?op=discuss&amp;id=1845724&amp;smallembed=1\" style=\"height: 300px; width: 100%; border: none;\"></iframe><img width='1' height='1' src='http://slashdot.feedsportal.com/c/32909/f/530758/s/f2c81d9/mf.gif' border='0'/><br/><br/><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/83965118980/u/49/f/530758/c/32909/s/f2c81d9/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/83965118980/u/49/f/530758/c/32909/s/f2c81d9/a2.img\" border=\"0\"/></a>
