 around 27 mph, the Audi A2 modified by DBM Energy was able to achieve its 375 miles range at an average speed of 55 mph.\"<p><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftech.slashdot.org%2Fstory%2F10%2F10%2F28%2F2258252%2FElectric-Car-Goes-375-Miles-On-One-6-Minute-Charge%3Ffrom%3Dfb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><img src=\"http://a.fsdn.com/sd/facebook_icon_large.png\"></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/home?status=Electric+Car+Goes+375+Miles+On+One+6-Minute+Charge%3A+http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fdj6LUw\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><img src=\"http://a.fsdn.com/sd/twitter_icon_large.png\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://tech.slashdot.org/story/10/10/28/2258252/Electric-Car-Goes-375-Miles-On-One-6-Minute-Charge?from=rss\">Read more of this story</a> at Slashdot.</p><iframe src=\"http://slashdot.org/slashdot-it.pl?op=discuss&amp;id=1844466&amp;smallembed=1\" style=\"height: 300px; width: 100%; border: none;\"></iframe><img width='1' height='1' src='http://slashdot.feedsportal.com/c/32909/f/530758/s/f24cf83/mf.gif' border='0'/><br/><br/><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/83964748699/u/49/f/530758/c/32909/s/f24cf83/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/83964748699/u/49/f/530758/c/32909/s/f24cf83/a2.img\" border=\"0\"/></a>
