altogether...\"<p><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.slashdot.org%2Fstory%2F10%2F10%2F29%2F1558231%2FThe-Galaxy-May-Have-Billions-of-Habitable-Planets%3Ffrom%3Dfb\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><img src=\"http://a.fsdn.com/sd/facebook_icon_large.png\"></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/home?status=The+Galaxy+May+Have+Billions+of+Habitable+Planets%3A+http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FcCn3iv\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><img src=\"http://a.fsdn.com/sd/twitter_icon_large.png\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://science.slashdot.org/story/10/10/29/1558231/The-Galaxy-May-Have-Billions-of-Habitable-Planets?from=rss\">Read more of this story</a> at Slashdot.</p><iframe src=\"http://slashdot.org/slashdot-it.pl?op=discuss&amp;id=1845644&amp;smallembed=1\" style=\"height: 300px; width: 100%; border: none;\"></iframe><img width='1' height='1' src='http://slashdot.feedsportal.com/c/32909/f/530758/s/f2c38c0/mf.gif' border='0'/><br/><br/><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/83965116895/u/49/f/530758/c/32909/s/f2c38c0/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/83965116895/u/49/f/530758/c/32909/s/f2c38c0/a2.img\" border=\"0\"/></a>
